    "cn/ lawru les/ rule/ allru les/ bussi ness/ t2016 0422_ 565143. html",
    "We chose this sample interval as follows: (1) Environmental responsibility data for many companies after 2020 are either unavailable or incomplete.",
    "(2) The COVID-19 caused a global pandemic after 2020, resulting in many outliers in the data.",
    "Therefore, we end our sample in 2020 in our main analysis.",
    "We use alternative data that ends in 2021 as a robustness check."
  ],
